* TEST 1:

* Input:

http://127.0.0.1:8080/

* Output:

<!DOCTYPE html>
    <html lang="en" dir="ltr">
      <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>Genome server</title>
      </head>
      <body style=" background-color: lightyellow;">
        <h1>Browsing Human and Vertebrates genome</h1>
        <p>BASIC Level Services</p>
        <form action="listSpecies" method="get">
          1) List of species in the genome database <br>Limit: <input type="text" name="limit">
          <br>
          <input type="submit" value="Send">
        </form>
        <form action="karyotype" method="get">
          2) Information about the karyotype <br>Select the species: <input type="text" name="specie">
          <br>
          <input type="submit" value="Send">
        </form>
        <form action="chromosomeLength" method="get">
          3) Chromosome length <br>Select the species: <input type="text" name="specie"><br>Select a chromosome: <input type="text" name="chromosome">
          <br>
          <input type="submit" value="Send">
          </form>
          <br>
        <p>MEDIUM Level Services</p>
        <form action="geneSeq" method="get">
          1) Enter a gene name or ID to find its sequence <br>Gene: <input type="text" name="gene">
          <br>
          <input type="submit" value="Send">
        </form>
        <form action="geneInfo" method="get">
          2) Enter a gene name or ID to find its basic info <br>Gene: <input type="text" name="gene">
          <br>
          <input type="submit" value="Send">
        </form>
        <form action="geneCalc" method="get">
          3) Enter a gene name or ID to perform some calculations <br>Gene: <input type="text" name="gene">
          <br>
          <input type="submit" value="Send">
        </form>
        </form>
      </body>
    </html>
